## Decisions and Action Items

*   **`draft-ietf-nfsv4-uncacheable-directories`:** **Chuck Lever** will open a second Working Group Last Call (WGLC) within 1 to 2 weeks to close out outstanding technical feedback.
*   **Security Draft:** The chairs will initiate a structured discussion and adoption call on the mailing list to determine if the security draft should be adopted, edited down, split, or folded back into the main `draft-ietf-nfsv4-rfc8881bis` document.
*   **Flex Files v2:** The call for adoption and the proposed document-split strategy will be taken to the mailing list.
*   **NFSv4.1 Respecification (`draft-ietf-nfsv4-rfc8881bis`):** Rather than scheduling an interim meeting, the chairs decided to prioritize moving the respecification discussion to the mailing list to encourage wider participation.

